    <h1>About LYIT Library</h1>
    <p>All LYIT students and staff automatically become members of their campus libraries. Your college ID card is also your library membership card. You will need your card for both the Issue desk and the Self Service Unit, located on the Letterkenny campus.</p>
    <ul class="fa-ul">
<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-check blue-txt"></i>Students can borrow 4 items at a time</li>
<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-check blue-txt"></i>Book loans can be renewed online at library.lyit.ie</li>
<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-check blue-txt"></i>Books and other library material may be borrowed for two weeks with up to 2 renewals allowed for some material</li>
<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-check blue-txt"></i>Theses and heavily used material are kept at the information desk and may be borrowed for up to 1 hours from Desk Reserve</li>
<li><i class="fa-li fa fa-check blue-txt"></i>Journals and Reference books can only be used in the library</li>
</ul>
